# {{context|countable|uncountable|lang=en}} The outer pod of the tiny fruit of a number of species in the genus ''[[Zanthoxylum]]'' widely grown and consumed in Asia as a spice. Not closely related to [[black pepper]] or to [[chilli pepper]]s.
# {{context|uncountable|lang=en}} [[spice|Spice]] made from this pod.
# {{context|countable|lang=en}} A plant producing the pods, ''Zanthoxylum''

